---
const title = "About Me";
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>{title} | Suifeng Wudong</title>
		<style>
			:root {
				--bg-color: #ffffff;
				--sidebar-bg: #f8fafc;
				--text-color: #1e293b;
				--text-muted: #64748b;
				--accent-color: #0284c7;
				--border-color: #e2e8f0;
				--max-width: 800px;
			}
			body {
				font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
				line-height: 1.6;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				background-color: var(--bg-color);
				color: var(--text-color);
			}
			.header {
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
				backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
				padding: 1rem 2rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				position: sticky;
				top: 0;
				z-index: 100;
			}
			.logo {
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				color: var(--accent-color);
				text-decoration: none;
			}
			.nav-links {
				display: flex;
				gap: 2rem;
			}
			.nav-links a {
				color: var(--text-muted);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
				transition: color 0.2s;
			}
			.nav-links a:hover {
				color: var(--accent-color);
			}
			.container {
				max-width: var(--max-width);
				margin: 4rem auto;
				padding: 0 2rem;
			}
			.profile-header {
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
				padding-bottom: 2rem;
			}
			.profile-header h1 {
				font-size: 3rem;
				margin: 0;
				color: #0f172a;
				letter-spacing: -0.025em;
			}
			.profile-header p {
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				margin-top: 0.5rem;
			}
			.content-section {
				margin-bottom: 4rem;
			}
			.content-section h2 {
				font-size: 1.75rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				color: #0f172a;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.75rem;
			}
			.content-section p {
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				font-size: 1.125rem;
				color: #334155;
			}
			.contact-list {
				list-style: none;
				padding: 0;
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
				gap: 1rem;
			}
			.contact-item {
				background: #f8fafc;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 0.25rem;
			}
			.contact-item span:first-child {
				font-size: 0.875rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.05em;
			}
			.contact-item a {
				color: var(--accent-color);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
				font-size: 1.125rem;
			}
			.contact-item a:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header class="header">
			<a href="/" class="logo">Suifeng Wudong</a>
			<nav class="nav-links">
				<a href="/">Home</a>
				<a href="/notes">Notes</a>
				<a href="/about">About</a>
			</nav>
		</header>

		<main class="container">
			<div class="profile-header">
				<h1>你好，我是 Suifeng Wudong</h1>
				<p>开发者 / 研究者 / 持续学习者</p>
			</div>

			<section class="content-section">
				<h2>关于我</h2>
				<p>我是一个热爱编程和技术的开发者。我喜欢探索新的技术和工具，并将它们应用到实际项目中，以解决现实世界的问题。</p>
				<p>目前，我对高性能计算、算法优化以及文档自动化技术有着浓厚的兴趣。在这个个人网站上，我记录了我的学术笔记（如运筹学）和工程实践心得。</p>
				<p>在业余时间，我喜欢阅读各种技术书籍，或者在 GitHub 上参与感兴趣的开源项目。我认为不断学习和分享是这个领域最让人兴奋的部分。</p>
			</section>

			<section class="content-section">
				<h2>联系方式</h2>
				<div class="contact-list">
					<div class="contact-item">
						<span>Email</span>
						<a href="mailto:HCXCNC@outlook.com">HCXCNC@outlook.com</a>
					</div>
					<div class="contact-item">
						<span>GitHub</span>
						<a href="https://github.com/suifengwudong" target="_blank">github.com/suifengwudong</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

